      "contents_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/mavam/pi-terminal-theme/contents/changelog%2Funreleased%2Finitial-release.md?ref=e7d7e394ae976dc4700f8d36035ac02117f87082",
      "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,19 @@\n+---\n+title: Add terminal theme\n+type: feature\n+author: mavam\n+created: 2026-02-28T09:59:50.751055Z\n+---\n+\n+Added a `terminal` theme for pi. Why?\n+\n+- Keeps pi aligned with your terminal's existing look.\n+- Avoids a mismatched color experience between pi and the rest of your terminal apps.\n+\n+How to use:\n+\n+```bash\n+pi install git:github.com/mavam/pi-terminal-theme\n+```\n+\n+Then select `terminal` in `/settings` under `theme`."
